The paper discusses the creation of general artificial intelligence through machine learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of meta-learning architectures (cs.LG), learning algorithms (cs.NE), and effective learning environments (cs.SE) to create an AI-generating algorithm. Additionally, the paper mentions safety and ethical considerations, which could fall under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SE, and cs.RO.
